WEBVTT

00:00:00.075 --> 00:00:35.166
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:07.875 --> 00:01:08.958
Xiao Liuzi

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:09.833
Hey

00:01:10.333 --> 00:01:14.625
Do you think I look like a great general?

00:01:14.958 --> 00:01:17.500
Foster Father is dignified and majestic, commanding respect everywhere.

00:01:17.625 --> 00:01:19.666
He truly has the bearing of Emperor Taizong.

00:01:23.916 --> 00:01:25.125
Foster Father

00:01:25.916 --> 00:01:27.250
Good

00:01:30.791 --> 00:01:31.708
Foster Father

00:01:34.333 --> 00:01:37.375
This Xuanyuan Mirror is an ancient artifact.

00:01:37.458 --> 00:01:39.916
It reveals the true form of all things in the world.

00:01:40.083 --> 00:01:43.208
I went through countless hardships to obtain it.

00:01:43.291 --> 00:01:45.500
Now, I present it to Foster Father.

00:01:56.583 --> 00:01:57.666
Ah, this...

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:02.291
Foster Father is truly destined by heaven.

00:02:04.583 --> 00:02:06.416
Everyone says

00:02:06.625 --> 00:02:09.166
Anyone can become emperor,

00:02:09.583 --> 00:02:11.208
except for me.

00:02:11.375 --> 00:02:13.416
Just because I am a eunuch.

00:02:13.625 --> 00:02:16.166
Yet this small Xuanyuan Mirror

00:02:16.333 --> 00:02:20.583
claims I have the bearing of a true dragon.

00:02:22.666 --> 00:02:25.166
This must be fate.

00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:40.250
Xiao Ran, Qiu Wan

00:02:40.708 --> 00:02:42.291
Let Luo Han take you to the inn to rest.

00:02:42.333 --> 00:02:43.791
I'll report to my adoptive father first.

00:02:44.625 --> 00:02:45.500
Yes

00:02:51.250 --> 00:02:52.375
Foster Father

00:02:52.541 --> 00:02:53.875
The spy has reported.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:57.416
The Hell Casino was also raided by the Cold Case Bureau.

00:02:58.041 --> 00:02:59.625
Lord Ghost King

00:03:00.541 --> 00:03:01.750
They say

00:03:02.458 --> 00:03:03.708
he is dead.

00:03:04.500 --> 00:03:05.833
What?

00:03:23.958 --> 00:03:25.291
Forget it.

00:03:26.375 --> 00:03:30.875
She was just unlucky in this life.

00:03:31.916 --> 00:03:36.375
She never got to see the day I fulfilled my dream.

00:03:36.500 --> 00:03:40.666
Standing with me at the top, overlooking the world.

00:03:42.791 --> 00:03:46.541
Find a good burial site for her.

00:03:46.666 --> 00:03:47.541
Yes

00:03:48.041 --> 00:03:50.416
What about those people from the Cold Case Bureau?

00:03:50.791 --> 00:03:53.541
Our men have been watching them since Chang'an County.

00:03:53.666 --> 00:03:56.916
They should be on their way back to the capital now.

00:03:56.958 --> 00:03:58.083
Good

00:03:58.375 --> 00:04:00.833
Keep a close watch on them.

00:04:01.125 --> 00:04:03.041
If anything happens,

00:04:03.166 --> 00:04:05.083
report to me immediately.

00:04:05.125 --> 00:04:05.833
Understood

00:04:05.875 --> 00:04:08.875
Also, what about that old King Kang?

00:04:09.166 --> 00:04:10.500
How is he now?

00:04:10.583 --> 00:04:11.958
Still the same as before.

00:04:12.041 --> 00:04:14.916
So sick he can barely get out of bed.

00:04:15.083 --> 00:04:18.000
He probably doesn't have much time left.

00:04:19.875 --> 00:04:22.291
Once I achieve my great ambition,

00:04:23.083 --> 00:04:29.750
I will definitely avenge Sheng Li.

00:04:34.833 --> 00:04:37.750
I've heard all about the gambling house.

00:04:38.041 --> 00:04:40.833
You must be tired from your journey back to the capital.

00:04:41.083 --> 00:04:43.083
Foster Father, there's something you don't know.

00:04:43.208 --> 00:04:44.750
The gambling house raided in Chang'an County

00:04:44.791 --> 00:04:46.875
was actually run by Eunuch Qiu.

00:04:47.666 --> 00:04:50.166
Qiu De, that man...

00:04:51.458 --> 00:04:53.666
Foster Father, please don't get upset.

00:04:54.541 --> 00:04:57.875
Qiu De is getting more and more brazen.

00:04:59.375 --> 00:05:00.458
Your Highness,

00:05:00.625 --> 00:05:02.125
Eunuch Qiu has acquired a treasure.

00:05:02.166 --> 00:05:04.541
They say the Xuanyuan Mirror has appeared.

00:05:04.833 --> 00:05:07.291
A grand palace banquet will be held in three days for this.

00:05:07.333 --> 00:05:09.333
All the royal family and nobles will attend.

00:05:09.583 --> 00:05:11.250
Master Dao Xuan will also be present.

00:05:12.583 --> 00:05:13.541
A palace banquet...

00:05:13.791 --> 00:05:16.708
Qiu De must be plotting something.

00:05:17.125 --> 00:05:18.208
From their conversation,

00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:22.500
it seems Eunuch Qiu saw the bearing of a true dragon in the Xuanyuan Mirror.

00:05:23.833 --> 00:05:24.958
Could it be...

00:05:25.583 --> 00:05:27.125
He wants to be emperor?

00:05:27.833 --> 00:05:30.500
That's why he's gathering all the Li Tang royals.

00:05:32.250 --> 00:05:35.666
A eunuch actually wants to usurp the throne.

00:05:38.625 --> 00:05:40.333
Ugh, this is so boring.

00:05:40.375 --> 00:05:41.541
Give me some of that.

00:05:41.666 --> 00:05:44.166
I didn't expect the capital to be so desolate now.

00:05:44.291 --> 00:05:45.250
Yeah.

00:05:45.750 --> 00:05:47.250
Might as well go back home.

00:05:48.125 --> 00:05:48.916
What do you mean?

00:05:48.916 --> 00:05:50.250
Are you trying to avoid paying me back?

00:05:50.750 --> 00:05:52.291
I don't have any money.

00:05:54.916 --> 00:05:57.416
Kind sirs, please help me.

00:05:57.500 --> 00:05:59.958
We haven't eaten in days.

00:06:00.166 --> 00:06:01.666
The child is too young.

00:06:01.708 --> 00:06:03.375
We've all been hungry for so long.

00:06:07.958 --> 00:06:09.000
I didn't bring any money.

00:06:10.416 --> 00:06:11.958
Please help me.

00:06:16.375 --> 00:06:17.083
Here.

00:06:17.083 --> 00:06:18.708
Thank you, thank you!

00:06:19.500 --> 00:06:21.833
Hey, Lin Xiaoran, didn't you say you had no money?

00:06:21.916 --> 00:06:22.750
No, I...

00:06:22.791 --> 00:06:24.166
You bastard!

00:06:25.166 --> 00:06:26.166
Watch where you're going!

00:06:26.208 --> 00:06:26.541
Sir!

00:06:26.541 --> 00:06:27.750
Selling these fakes...

00:06:28.125 --> 00:06:29.583
And who the hell are you?

00:06:29.875 --> 00:06:30.708
How dare you cause trouble here!

00:06:30.791 --> 00:06:32.416
A good dog doesn't block the way.

00:06:32.541 --> 00:06:33.083
Get out of my way.

00:06:33.083 --> 00:06:35.000
Hey, watch your mouth, Eunuch.

00:06:35.083 --> 00:06:37.666
Look, this eunuch is hitting people in the street!

00:06:37.750 --> 00:06:39.750
Smashing things and not paying for them, see?

00:06:44.125 --> 00:06:46.375
Thank you, sirs! Thank you!

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.833
Why didn't he let you sell that mirror just now?

00:06:49.375 --> 00:06:50.833
You two may not know,

00:06:51.041 --> 00:06:52.458
but it's all over the cityâ€”

00:06:52.583 --> 00:06:54.958
they say the Xuanyuan Mirror can reveal one's true form and soul.

00:06:55.083 --> 00:06:56.333
It can tell loyalty from treachery, good from evil.

00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:59.833
I just wanted to make a little money off the hype.

00:07:01.333 --> 00:07:02.500
If they won't let me sell, then so be it.

00:07:02.666 --> 00:07:04.791
Thank you, sirs.

00:07:07.541 --> 00:07:09.333
A mirror that can reveal the soul...

00:07:09.500 --> 00:07:11.416
Lin Xiaoran, what do you think about this?

00:07:12.083 --> 00:07:14.166
Let's go back to the Cold Case Bureau and find Li Jingnian first.

00:07:16.166 --> 00:07:17.375
Foster Father has already found out

00:07:17.708 --> 00:07:20.041
that the one who ordered Guo Huai, Yu Ming, and the other soldiers

00:07:20.208 --> 00:07:23.166
to secretly alter the Tang dynasty's dragon veins at the border

00:07:23.333 --> 00:07:24.708
was Eunuch Qiu.

00:07:25.666 --> 00:07:28.208
So the owner we found at the Ghost Brothel in Luoyang's Liuxiang Pavilion

00:07:28.208 --> 00:07:29.375
was also that old eunuch.

00:07:29.416 --> 00:07:30.250
That's right.

00:07:30.333 --> 00:07:32.208
The one behind the Chang'an gambling house

00:07:32.500 --> 00:07:33.625
was also Eunuch Qiu.

00:07:33.708 --> 00:07:34.791
So that means,

00:07:34.875 --> 00:07:36.375
when we were in Fuping County,

00:07:36.500 --> 00:07:39.458
the rare book "Treatise on Ruling the Nation" that Magistrate Sun sent from Chang'an

00:07:39.500 --> 00:07:41.000
was also meant for Eunuch Qiu.

00:07:41.041 --> 00:07:43.375
That old eunuch's ambition is obvious now.

00:07:43.666 --> 00:07:45.500
And now there's this Xuanyuan Mirror incident.

00:07:45.833 --> 00:07:47.000
The current situation

00:07:47.208 --> 00:07:48.541
is like a storm about to break.

00:07:48.666 --> 00:07:52.791
It's a pity the people believe in the Xuanyuan Mirror so deeply.

00:07:52.875 --> 00:07:54.166
In these troubled times,

00:07:54.208 --> 00:07:56.875
everyone wishes for a savior to rescue them from misery.

00:07:57.625 --> 00:07:59.125
I've roamed the martial world for years,

00:07:59.166 --> 00:08:01.166
and never heard of anything like the Xuanyuan Mirror.

00:08:01.250 --> 00:08:02.708
There must be some plot behind this.

00:08:02.708 --> 00:08:03.916
Whatever the plot is,

00:08:04.166 --> 00:08:05.791
the only thing we can do now

00:08:06.208 --> 00:08:07.666
is to enter the palace and get the mirror.

00:08:07.958 --> 00:08:10.875
So Eunuch Qiu's plans will be ruined.

00:08:11.541 --> 00:08:12.625
That's one way.

00:08:13.458 --> 00:08:14.958
But if we want to enter the palace,

00:08:15.541 --> 00:08:17.000
we'll need someone with a fresh face.

00:08:23.083 --> 00:08:24.958
Aren't we the only new faces here?

00:08:26.166 --> 00:08:27.375
Alright, let's go get the mirror.

00:08:27.416 --> 00:08:28.166
Then, what about you?

00:08:28.250 --> 00:08:29.958
I'll go check on Foster Father Qiu's movements.

00:08:30.125 --> 00:08:31.083
After it's done,

00:08:31.500 --> 00:08:32.833
I'll meet you at the south gate.

00:08:35.583 --> 00:08:36.791
This is the token to enter the palace.

00:08:39.625 --> 00:08:40.541
A token.

00:08:42.166 --> 00:08:44.333
It's good to be an official.

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:46.458
We do all the dirty and tiring work.

00:08:48.166 --> 00:08:51.000
So, can we get paid a bit more for this?

00:08:51.500 --> 00:08:52.375
No problem.

00:08:53.458 --> 00:08:54.625
Generous.

00:08:57.041 --> 00:09:00.333
His Majesty is about to grow up soon.

00:09:00.791 --> 00:09:03.791
Why can't I understand this book?

00:09:04.250 --> 00:09:06.125
Pick it up for me.

00:09:06.333 --> 00:09:08.458
Yes, Foster Father.

00:09:21.583 --> 00:09:23.833
Li Jingnian got on the carriage an hour ago.

00:09:23.875 --> 00:09:26.416
He's on his way to the palace now.

00:09:26.625 --> 00:09:28.541
Is he alone?

00:09:28.750 --> 00:09:31.041
What about his men?

00:09:31.125 --> 00:09:33.166
After leaving the prince's residence,

00:09:33.416 --> 00:09:35.000
they went in another direction.

00:09:35.041 --> 00:09:36.333
Their whereabouts are unknown.

00:10:00.416 --> 00:10:03.208
Shen Qiuwan, these are the clothes you wanted.

00:10:03.416 --> 00:10:05.166
You're lucky to even get to wear this.

00:10:05.208 --> 00:10:06.458
And you're still being picky.

00:10:25.750 --> 00:10:28.125
Hey, you two, wait a moment.

00:10:37.583 --> 00:10:40.333
Come, look! This eunuch is beating someone in public.